# RCA Mandatory Sections

RCA drafts must include all of the following sections before scrutiny proceeds:

1. Incident summary
2. Impact
3. Timeline
4. Root cause
5. Solution
6. Action items
7. Mitigation plan

If any section is missing:
- Stop progression.
- Explicitly request only missing information.
- Resume workflow only after completion.
